# WawaUI

A simple and lightweight Roblox UI library.

## Features

- Clean interface
- Multiple tabs
- Toggle elements

## Loading the Library

```lua
local Library = loadstring(game:HttpGet("https://raw.githubusercontent.com/wawathegreat/WawaUi/main/WawaUI.lua"))()
```

## Creating a Window

```lua
local Window = Library.CreateWindow("My Script")
```

## Themes

```lua
Window:SetTheme("Dark")
Window:SetTheme("White")
Window:SetTheme("Midnight")
```